title: Le Mans Legends 2013: Chris Harris Drives a Lister Jaguar Coupe -- /DRIVE MOMENTS
description: Wet.Dry. Wet again. With some dry bits. But also some wet. I'd done 6 laps of the circuit before the race. The car is worth £2m and this was easily the biggest driving challenge of my life. VMax on the straight is around 180mph.
